import numpy as np
import plotly.graph_objs as go
from plotly.offline import init_notebook_mode, iplot

init_notebook_mode(connected=True)  

#   
T_DUR = 2  # , 
F = 6  # , 
N_SAMP_PER_PERIOD = 20  #      

f_samp = N_SAMP_PER_PERIOD * F

x = np.linspace(0, T_DUR, T_DUR * f_samp)
y = np.sin(F * x * 2 * np.pi)

fig = go.Figure(
    data=[go.Scatter(x=x, y=y)],
    layout_title_text="  ",
    layout_xaxis_title=", ",
)
iplot(fig)
fig = go.Figure(
    data=[go.Bar(y=np.abs(np.fft.fft(y, n=f_samp, norm="forward")))],
    layout_title_text=" ",
    layout_xaxis_title="  ()",
)
iplot(fig)

import numpy as np
import plotly.graph_objs as go
from plotly.offline import init_notebook_mode, iplot

init_notebook_mode(connected=True)  

#   
T_DUR = 1  # , 
F = 6  # , 
N_SAMP_PER_PERIOD = 100  #      
FIRST_AMP = 2  #   
SECOND_AMP = 1  #   

f_samp = N_SAMP_PER_PERIOD * F

x = np.linspace(0, T_DUR, T_DUR * f_samp)
y = FIRST_AMP * np.sin(F * x * 2 * np.pi)
y = y + SECOND_AMP * np.sin(2 * F * x * 2 * np.pi)

fig = go.Figure(
    data=[go.Scatter(x=x, y=y)],
    layout_title_text="  ",
    layout_xaxis_title=", ",
)
iplot(fig)
fig = go.Figure(
    data=[go.Bar(y=np.abs(np.fft.fft(y, n=f_samp, norm="forward")))],
    layout_title_text=" ",
    layout_xaxis_title="  ()",
)
iplot(fig)

In[40]:
import numpy as np
import plotly.graph_objs as go
from plotly.offline import init_notebook_mode, iplot

init_notebook_mode(connected=True)  

#   
T_DUR = 1  # , 
F = 1  # , 
N_TONES = 200  #  
N_SAMP_PER_PERIOD = 100  #      

f_samp = N_SAMP_PER_PERIOD * N_TONES * F

x = np.linspace(0, T_DUR, T_DUR * f_samp)
y = np.sin(F * x * 2 * np.pi)
for i in range(2, 200):
    y = y + np.sin(i * F * x * 2 * np.pi)

fig = go.Figure(
    data=[go.Scatter(x=x, y=y)],
    layout_title_text="  ",
    layout_xaxis_title=", ",
)
iplot(fig)
fig = go.Figure(
    data=[go.Bar(y=np.abs(np.fft.fft(y, n=f_samp, norm="forward")))],
    layout_title_text=" ",
    layout_xaxis_title="  ()",
    layout=go.Layout(xaxis=dict(range=[0, 1000])),
)
iplot(fig)

import numpy as np
import plotly.graph_objs as go
from plotly.offline import init_notebook_mode, iplot

init_notebook_mode(connected=True)  

#   
T_DUR = 1  # , 
F = 6  #   , 
F_AM = 20 * F  #  , 
N_SAMP_PER_PERIOD = 100  #      

f_samp = N_SAMP_PER_PERIOD * F_AM

x = np.linspace(0, T_DUR, T_DUR * f_samp)
y = np.sin(F * x * 2 * np.pi) + 2
y = y * np.cos(F_AM * x * 2 * np.pi)

fig = go.Figure(
    data=[go.Scatter(x=x, y=y)],
    layout_title_text="  ",
    layout_xaxis_title=", ",
)
iplot(fig)
fig = go.Figure(
    data=[go.Bar(y=np.abs(np.fft.fft(y, n=f_samp, norm="forward")))],
    layout_title_text=" ",
    layout_xaxis_title="  ()",
    layout=go.Layout(xaxis=dict(range=[0, 2 * F_AM])),
)
iplot(fig)

import numpy as np
import plotly.graph_objs as go
from plotly.offline import init_notebook_mode, iplot

init_notebook_mode(connected=True)  

#   
T_DUR = 1  # , 
N_SAMP_PER_PERIOD = 50  #      
F_START = 1  #  , 
F_END = 50  #  , 

f_samp = N_SAMP_PER_PERIOD * F_END

x = np.linspace(0, T_DUR, T_DUR * f_samp)
chirp = np.linspace(F_START / (np.pi / 2), F_END / (np.pi / 2), len(x))
y = np.sin(chirp * x * 2 * np.pi)

fig = go.Figure(
    data=[go.Scatter(x=x, y=y)],
    layout_title_text="  ",
    layout_xaxis_title=", ",
)
iplot(fig)
fig = go.Figure(
    data=[go.Bar(y=np.abs(np.fft.fft(y, n=f_samp, norm="forward")))],
    layout_title_text=" ",
    layout_xaxis_title="  ()",
    layout=go.Layout(xaxis=dict(range=[0, 1000])),
)
iplot(fig)
